    <name>Unit 3 Video</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p&gt;For this video, you will need the Unit 3 Handouts located here or on the main course page. These handouts include the &lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-3-integ-skil-les-com-eng.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Unit 3: Pause and Think Handout&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-3-overview-com-appr.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Overview of Communicatively Based Approaches&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-3-overview-com-prac-act.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Overview of Communicative Practice Activities&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-3-obs-les-anal-guide.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Lesson Observation Guide&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-3-sam-read-less-plan.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Personality and Birth-order Reading Lesson Plan&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-3-samp-gram-less-plan.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Contextualized Grammar Lesson Plan&lt;/a&gt;, and the &lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit-3-integ-skil-les-com-eng.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Community Engagement Integrated Skills Lesson Plan&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;For the fillable PDFs, please be sure to save your PDF before closing the document in order to keep your notes. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Finally, please &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2022-03/unit3-transcr.pdf" target="_blank" style="font-size: 1.7rem; background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;click here to access the video and visual transcripts.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After you view this presentation, return to the main course page to complete a short knowledge check and to find the Unit References and Recommended Resources. See you in Unit &lt;a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a&gt;4.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
